article.description: — Xavier Dusell had 29 points in Fresno State's 68-66 win over Air Force on Saturday night.
article.headline: Dusell scores 29 as Fresno State knocks off Air Force 68-66
article.linkText: Dusell scores 29 as Fresno State knocks off Air Force 68-66
article.story: AIR FORCE ACADEMY, Colo. -- — Xavier Dusell had 29 points in Fresno State's 68-66 win over Air Force on Saturday night. Dusell shot 8 for 11 (7 for 8 from 3-point range) and 6 of 6 from the free throw line for the Bulldogs (11-13, 4-7 Mountain West Conference). Jalen Weaver scored 16 points, going 6 of 11 from the floor, including 1 for 3 from 3-point range, and 3 for 3 from the line. Isaiah Hill finished 7 of 13 from the field to finish with 14 points. Weaver's basket with 1:13 left snapped a tie and the Bulldogs held on from there. Jeffrey Mills led the Falcons (8-15, 1-10) in scoring, finishing with 20 points and two steals. Beau Becker added 17 points and two blocks for Air Force. In addition, Rytis Petraitis had 14 points, 11 rebounds, six assists and five steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
